description	"Alderaanian Consular Security Officer

^2Weaponry:
- DH-17 Blaster Pistol (3)
-- Automatic Mode [E-11]

^8Attributes:
- Reinforcements (1)
- Ammo Drop [Press Use to Drop Ammo]

Made up of men and women who served as security for Alderaanian Diplomats, these men and woman have sworn to lay down their lives to protect Princess Leia Organa so that she can complete her mission for the rebellion.
Many of these served as members of the Alliance to Restore the Republic"